      <title>人民币投资者紧张不安，因中国假期可能引发波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/yuan-investors-on-edge-as-china-s-holiday-may-spur-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国明显暂缓受到美国更严厉的关税影响，但投资者仍然对人民币持怀疑态度，担心在即将到来的为期一周的交易假期期间及之后可能出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/yuan-investors-on-edge-as-china-s-holiday-may-spur-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省养老金管理机构重组，裁减 DEI 职位及其他 18 个职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/alberta-pension-cuts-dei-role-and-18-other-jobs-amid-shakeup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月前，加拿大阿尔伯塔投资管理公司（Alberta Investment Management Corp.）下令对这家养老基金管理公司进行改组，并解雇了其首席执行官和董事会，随后，该公司在非投资领域裁减了 19 个工作岗位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/alberta-pension-cuts-dei-role-and-18-other-jobs-amid-shakeup</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 22:59:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福蒂斯丘收购红鹰矿业以开采西澳大利亚矿石</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/fortescue-to-buy-red-hawk-mining-to-tap-western-australia-ore</link>
      <description><![CDATA[福蒂斯丘有限公司 (Fortescue Ltd.) 计划收购红鹰矿业有限公司 (Red Hawk Mining Ltd.)，以获得位于西澳大利亚其主要所罗门项目附近的一处未开发铁矿的使用权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/fortescue-to-buy-red-hawk-mining-to-tap-western-australia-ore</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 22:51:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股市崩盘后，亚洲市场准备迎接人工智能的冲击：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于推动牛市发展的人工智能领域出现裂痕，华尔街经历了一段艰难的时期，亚洲交易员们准备迎接周二的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 22:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股指期货下跌，芯片公司可能因 DeepSeek 延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/japan-stock-futures-fall-chip-firms-may-extend-drop-on-deepseek</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股指期货下跌，由于对中国人工智能初创公司 DeepSeek 的担忧引发美国科技股暴跌，芯片相关股票有望延续周一的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/japan-stock-futures-fall-chip-firms-may-extend-drop-on-deepseek</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 22:47:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
