    <item>
      <title>Quantify Funds 首席执行官谈 STKD 比特币和黄金 ETF (BTGD)</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/quantify-funds-ceo-on-stkd-bitcoin-gold-etf-btgd-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于比特币和黄金被视为稀缺资产，人们经常投资它们来防范全球货币贬值，Quantify Funds 首席执行官兼首席信息官 David Dziekanski 表示，将它们合二为一是有价值的。他在“ETF IQ”上解释了 STKD 比特币和黄金 ETF（股票代码：BTGD）。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/quantify-funds-ceo-on-stkd-bitcoin-gold-etf-btgd-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 21:15:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普意外发起关税战 引发哥伦比亚股市抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-sparks-colombia-selloff-with-unexpected-tariff-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于哥伦比亚突然（尽管是短暂的）与其长期政治盟友和最大贸易伙伴美国陷入关税战，哥伦比亚比索大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-sparks-colombia-selloff-with-unexpected-tariff-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 13:06:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥比索兑日元汇率创 8 月以来最大单日跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/emerging-assets-fall-on-trump-s-tariff-tactics-tech-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国贸易政策走向的担忧以及避险推动日元上涨，墨西哥周一领跌新兴市场货币，迫使投资者平仓由日元资助的套利交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/emerging-assets-fall-on-trump-s-tariff-tactics-tech-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 10:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市暴跌，人工智能敲响警钟：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，华尔街开局并不顺利，因为人们担心中国初创公司 DeepSeek 的廉价人工智能模型可能会让推动牛市的技术的估值变得难以合理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 22:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
